default4.3
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultDisproportionate impact:default The Government has been unable to provide figures on the number of young people likely to be excluded on account of the residence test. However, new immigrants tend to be disproportionately young and it is clear from reported cases that unaccompanied mino
defaultrs have some of the most pressing 
defaultlegal needs. Even where children and young people would technically qualify under the test, from our experience it is clear that young people are less likely to be able to provide proof of lawful residence.  Young people w
defaultho have the greatest level of legal need often come from the most chaotic backgrounds and will have the greatest difficulty in providing documentary evidence of lawful residence, even if they qualify for it. There appear to be no special considerations as 
defaultto how children who qualify will be assisted to jump through the residence test. The burden of proof will be on the provider. Overstretched legal aid providers are unlikely to have the time and resources to go the extra mile (without payment) to assist you
defaultng people to obtain proof of residence. Those that do not qualify will be without any a
defaultssistance or access to justice.
default It should be noted that children and young people are a protected group and at risk of discrimination
default.
default 
default&#xa0;defaultCase studydefault: GdefaultG aged 6 settled
default 
default(lawfully) in the UK with her mother
default,
default 
defaultwho is married to a mem
defaultber of the Brigade of Gurkhas. 
defaultHer father subjected her mother to a vicious assault (for which he was charged).  She and her mother fled the house and then accessed legal assistance to secure a
defaultn injunction and then divorce. 
defaultThe combination of the rules under LASPO and the residence test would provide two difficult hurdles for G’s mother to overcome in order to protect herself and her
default 6 year old child 
defaultfrom witnessing domestic violence
default.
default 
